Carlton vs Collingwood AFL Live
Round 03
Date: 13 Apr 2012                                                                 
Melbourne Cricket Ground Stadium, 07:50 pm

Carlton and Collingwood will renew their celebrated rivalry in front of a packed house at the MCG on the big stage of Friday night football. Despite a lengthy injury list, the Pies are still considered one of the favourites for the flag, but the Blues will be desperate to establish their own premiership credentials with a win.